untukmu, tuan putri.

00:03:55.727 --> 00:03:57.095
Pelayan...

00:03:59.398 --> 00:04:00.922
Siapa namamu?

00:04:01.072 --> 00:04:03.198
Um... Shaina.  Lihat!

00:04:03.388 --> 00:04:05.071
